              "free_text": [
                " Experiment performed at the Intense",
                "Pulsed Neutron Source (IPNS) at Argonne National",
                "Laboratory."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Three sapphire (aluminium oxide A1203) samples of",
                "premium 'hemex' grade, which is highest available",
                "grade of sapphire and is almost free of lattice",
                "distortion were used in experiment at ambient",
                "temperature. The size of each of the crystals was",
                "25.4 x 25.4 x 27.0 mm3, with the c axis parallel to",
                "the 27.0 mm edge. The faces perpendicular to the c",
                "axis were optically polished."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BF3",
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The measurements were recorded as a",
                "function of time of flight using two flat ('pancake')",
                "detectors, low-efficiency BF3 ionization chambers,",
                "placed before the collimation and after the sample at",
                "distances of 5.9 and 9.0m, respectively, from the",
                "liquid-hydrogen moderator."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HE3SP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "An additional He3 detector was placed",
                "immediately after the second pancake BF3 detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "TRN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The source operated at 30 Hz. Total cross",
                "section measured using transmission method"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "SPALL"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Neutrons were produced by 450 MeV protons",
                "impinging on enriched uranium target. The neutron",
                "transmission measurements were obtained on the C3",
                "beam line, which views a 20K liquid-hydrogen moderator.",
                "Delayed neutron fraction was 0.0283 which results in a",
                "time-independent background, The spectrum peaks around",
                "0.25 nm, indicating an effective moderator temperature",
                "of 60 K"
              ]
            }
          ],
